%
O0001
; THE BEAST - 0.5" Radius Circle, 0.1" Deep
; Feed Rate: 100 in/min | Plunge: 80 in/min | Spindle: 22000 RPM

G20        ; Inches mode
G90        ; Absolute mode
G91        ; Relative positioning
S22000     ; Spindle speed
M3         ; Spindle ON
G4 P2      ; Dwell 2 seconds - let spindle spin up
F80        ; Plunge rate
G1 Z-0.1  ; Plunge down 0.1 inches
F100       ; Feed rate
G1 X0.5   ; Move to circle start (right side of center)
G2 I-0.5 J0 ; Full circle clockwise back to start
G1 X-0.5  ; Return to center
F80        ; Plunge rate for Z return
G1 Z0.1   ; Raise Z back to original height
M5         ; Spindle OFF
G90        ; Return to absolute positioning
M30        ; End program and rewind
%
